=== SHADOW_WRITING ===
# id: 61
# title: The Shadow Writing
# chinese_title: 影字
# category: Puzzle
# mode: dungeon

In a darkened room, characters appear only as shadows cast by a moving light source. The shadows spell out a passphrase, but the light moves quickly. You must read the characters before the light completes its circuit and the room goes dark again.

* [Focus and read the shadow characters quickly]
  ~ gain_radical("目")
  "影" (yǐng) — shadow, reflection. Related to "目" (mù) — eye.
* [Use your suit's recording system to slow the playback]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "慢" (màn) — slow
* [Illuminate the room with your own light]
  ~ gain_item("scanner_pulse")
  "亮" (liàng) — bright, clear
